{"tid":1598983,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[外銷文宣] 好癲，終於有首唱得出（仲唱埋嘅）法文版《榮光》啦！","createTime":"2019-09-27T17:27:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-28T20:22:36.000Z","uid":259035,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"e5117d49bfc8037b8e55be4aa80fd0db819afd98","tid":1598983,"uid":259035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T17:27:10.000Z","msg":"好癲，喺加拿大魁省嘅巴打已經創譯咗唱得出嘅法語版歌詞！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\">YOUTUBE　歌詞版MV：</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/cGfjaBjP7Os\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FcGfjaBjP7Os&d=MLRnjlmMEh1el5UvTt2rHWzUwbN2nhMFbUYjFdDHJd4%3D&h=61a6fbee\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/cGfjaBjP7Os</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: purple;\">一齊跟住唱：</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Que la gloire soit &agrave; Hong Kong （願榮光歸香港）</span><br />\nby Montreal Guy<br />\n<br />\nPourquoi pleure-t-elle toujours, cette terre?<br />\nPourquoi tout le monde est en col&egrave;re?<br />\nLevons la t&ecirc;te, levons la voix, que nos cris soient forts<br />\nVive la libert&eacute; sur terre!<br />\n何以 這土地 淚再流<br />\n何以 令眾人 亦憤恨<br />\n昂首 拒默沉 吶喊聲 響透<br />\n盼自由 歸於 這裡<br />\n<br />\nPourquoi ne s&rsquo;efface pas cette peur?<br />\nPourquoi suivrons-nous tous nos c&oelig;urs? <br />\nPourquoi s&rsquo;avancer m&ecirc;me couverts de sang?  <br />\nPour un Hong Kong glorieux!<br />\n何以 這恐懼 抹不走<br />\n何以 為信念 從沒退後<br />\n何解 血在流 但邁進聲 響透<br />\n建自由 光輝 香港<br />\n<br />\nLes &eacute;toiles tombent dans la nuit <br />\nLe signal dans la brume nous rassemble tous <br />\nD&eacute;fendons notre libert&eacute; de toutes nos forces<br />\nCourage! Sagesse! Ne mourront jamais!<br />\n在晚星 墜落 徬徨午夜<br />\n迷霧裡 最遠處吹來 號角聲<br />\n捍自由 來齊集這裡 來全力抗對<br />\n勇氣 智慧 也永不滅<br />\n<br />\nLe jour se l&egrave;ve, r&eacute;tablissons notre Hong Kong <br />\nLes Citoyens! Battons-nous pour la justice, <br />\nD&eacute;mocratie! Libert&eacute;! Qu&rsquo;elles soient &eacute;ternelles!<br />\nQue la gloire soit &agrave; Hong Kong!<br />\n黎明來到 要光復 這香港<br />\n同行兒女 為正義 時代革命<br />\n祈求 民主與自由 萬世都不朽<br />\n我願榮光歸香港 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yTZDVAC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyTZDVAC.jpg&h=b298597f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nLyric Graphic Version: <a href=\"https://buff.ly/2mXoBe2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbuff.ly%2F2mXoBe2&d=MLRnjlmMEh1el5UvTt2rHWzUwbN2nhMFbUYjFdDHJd4%3D&h=b3882afd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://buff.ly/2mXoBe2</a>"},{"pid":"6e14dcb41e59e55c4a75b637bb05722e0047f97a","tid":1598983,"uid":66049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T17:31:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c26ad4df84a13771dcfe850d1e7873d4c501859","tid":1598983,"uid":325346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T17:32:48.000Z","msg":"勁到七彩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a76facf653329e7fb75bf1df08c2876c53a714da","tid":1598983,"uid":132859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T17:40:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e53037612c43d881b65fd0640bee5e9ab1b7f4e4","tid":1598983,"uid":70973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T18:29:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81613671f23f71627c20ff15a45d8647a08baca6","tid":1598983,"uid":24612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T04:23:48.000Z","msg":"問隔離個法國妹，佢話唔明<br />\n再問多兩個，明明哋"},{"pid":"ba926d07141136d6a